creator: Lojika
descriptionHtml: Morning sunshine turns into a dark storm with hails size of a tennis ball! Subway never fails to be the fastest mode of transportation unless it’s closed due to terror attack! Snow halts all transportation system, you envy SUVs while freezing at bus stop. Everyday some darkness covers your head and leaves you alone in the middle of terrifying urban disaster.  Why stay alone as a tiny little dot in such huge universe? Your friends in good times might be your heroes in dark times. Go find them in TAG! Your colleagues, neighbours, school mates, anyone who is in the same route as you daily, would be you ride-mate via TAG. Build your trusted transportation network with these buddies in good times, connect, meet and become resilient in tough times! So if you also think that; • Busses, metro-busses, metros and trams are just making you feel like canned sardines during rush hours • Your car consumes all your income • You get muscle spasms because of driving in traffic; Ride along with a friend, share the costs and ride in style! Share your car with your friends, let them ride in comfort by just paying their petrol share. This means 1/5 of the taxi cost! For the comfort of your car, the joy of your company this is a price they are willing to pay with no doubt! And soon you will forget the expense of petrol and no longer feel trapped in traffic.
descriptionShort: TAG ride-mates are by your side for safer & economical commute, never ride alone

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Health workers and Corona period heroes have to go to work every day. We wanted to make them connect with each other more easily. Now, you may share your prospecting trip details via social media and Whatsapp to reach more friends and colleagues.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Now on, TAG is called SeatX!
We prepared a lovely update for you. You may join secure hitchhike networks with your friends from work, school, and social circle. All you need is to confirm your work-school email.
You may share your trip info on social media, or send it directly to your friends on Whatsapp. Then, they may join your trip with one click.
Some reminders about "the new normal": Mask, sanitizer, and open-window trips! Isolate yourself and friends from public transportation and join us.

title: TAGmobil for daily ridesharing

creator: Lojika
descriptionHtml:
SeatX is your trusted hitchhike network of friends, friends of friends, professional contacts, neighbours and others. Find them, hitchhike with them, and chip in for the costs.

Hitchhiking with SeatX has more. SeatX can save lives. With SeatX, you're never alone in snowstorms, floods, hurricanes, earthquakes or empty roads during the night as you are the part of a supportive network for sharing. Make SeatX part of your daily routine. You and your beloved ones will be supported during difficult times.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Generous prizes for frequenters! All the answers are waiting for you ahead.
You may also share your ride not in cars, but also in yellow cabs, motobikes, zeplins, UFOs... We trust your creativity.
